title: Straw Hat Pirates bounties after Dressrosa Arc? : r/OnePiece - Reddit
body: It was only one or two weeks ago in the One Piece timeline, and we've not heard any increases yet. Potentially their influence in Fishman Island combined with their actions on Punk Hazard and (for some) Dressarosa, will give all the gang new bounties. [deleted] • 9 yr. ago.
